cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is the most likely category as the paper deals with personalized recommendation of items based on user's past interactions. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new recommendation model that uses convolutional neural networks for learning sequential patterns. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is another possible category as the paper deals with natural language processing of user-item interactions. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possible category as the paper uses the concept of image embedding to represent the sequence of items. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a new AI-based recommendation model.
